TEMPLATE 1
Randomly synthesize template containing questions, answers and solutions from separated question, answer and solution files.
Each mmd file (each page) consists of from 3 to 4 questions with corresponding answers and solutions.

TEMPLATE 2
Randomly synthesize template containing questions from separated question files.
Each mmd file (each page) consists of from 2 to 8 questions.

TEMPLATE 3
Randomly synthesize template containing questions and solutions from separated question and solution files.
Each mmd file (each page) consists of from 2 to 3 questions with corresponding solutions.

TEMPLATE 4
Randomly synthesize template containing questions and answers from separated question and answer files.
Each mmd file (each page) consists of from 2 to 10 questions with corresponding answers.
